episodes.title: Kylar Aaron - Escaping A Cult and Healing Emotional Trauma and PTSD
episodes.description:
Kylar Aaron is a wellness and hope coach who specialises in trauma recovery, empath empowerment, and healing transformation. He works with those who have suffered stunning setbacks to facilitate gentle restoration to their most Authentic and vibrant selves.

Kylar's life is a story of transformation. After a childhood living in a cult he developed Complex PTSD and accumulated multiple health issues, Kylar became obsessed with positive life change. 

His journey of healing, connection, and transformation led him into life coaching, massage therapy, and fitness training.

His message is to hope for living fully alive, no matter your past experiences and traumas.

Kylar is passionate about helping people to heal from their past and live their authentic lives to the fullest. 

Check out Kylar's website at: https://kylarwellness.com
